data.name: Alien Samurai Dino Warriors
data.description:
**A unique NFT collectible collection based on the forthcoming graphic novel created by #1 DJ Dimitri Vegas, with the originator and executive producer of the BATMAN Movie Universe, Michael Uslan and his son David**

_Millions of years ago, Dinosaurs went extinct forever and mammals took over the planet. At least, that’s as far as we know…_

_After being frozen underground for thousands of years, a group of dinosaurs from another universe must master martial arts – and how to be modern-day teenagers – in order to defend the place they now call home, earth._

The book is written by Dimitri Vegas himself, in collaboration with Erik Burnham (Ghostbusters, Back To The Future, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles). Together with a formidable team artists and Hollywood creatives, ASDW aims to grow into a potential multi-medium crossover brand and claim it's place in pop culture history.

Welcome to the #DinoVerse 🦖

data.name: Altitude Lodge
data.description:
## Altitude Lodge

The Altitude Lodge has all the gear you need to prepare for your journey through the Altitude Slopes and Avalanche! Shred some PWDR with our limited-edition, equippable NFTs to level up your farming boosts and flash loan discounts throughout the Altitude Ecosystem!

*NFTs must be deposited in our Loyalty contract to be eligible for bonuses. Only one bonus per account.*

# PWDR Snowboards - Series 1

The first set of Lodge NFTs are the **PWDR Snowboards**. You'll be pulling off some serious tricks with these! Created to commemorate the PWDR Liquidity Generation Event (LGE). The Golden, Silver, and Bronze Snowboard were created in limited quantities and awarded to LGE participants. Snowboards grant boost which increases Farming Total Value Locked (TVL) and further discounts Flash Loan fees.

Learn more about Altitude: https://altitude.finance/

data.name: AltNouns
data.description:
One Alt Noun, every day, forever.

An **occ🛠️experiment **.

The first never-ending, completely on-chain art derivative of Nouns. Each Alt Noun is made from very the Noun it is based on. The Alt Nouns contract talks with the Nouns contract and generates an Alt Noun from this conversation. As long as there are Nouns, there will be Alt Nouns.

No ipfs/arweave, no rendering script. Just contracts talking to each other on the Ethereum Blockchain.

[Alt Nouns](https://occ.xyz/altnouns) | [@onChainCo](https://twitter.com/onChainCo)

data.name: Andreas Wannerstedt
data.description: Andreas Wannerstedt is a Stockholm based digital artist and art director who crafts unique 3D sculptures and mesmerizing looping animations. The imagery of Andreas is both sophisticated and whimsical, and his synchronised animations has often been described as “oddly satisfying”, since the overall effect often evokes a strangely hypnotizing feeling. It’s all about interactions between shape and space, a portal into the perfect world of physics, movement, and predictability. During the last 15 years he’s been doing commissioned work for many of the worlds most recognisable brands and his animations have fascinated millions of viewers around the world.

A collection previously thought to be lost by the MOMB, given out exclusively to holders of Borpacasso- for free (just pay gas).

MoMB blends popular internet culture with fine art precedents, subverting the art canon to develop an entirely new and widely recognizable NFT artform. Specifically, Borpa’s abstractionist quality is married to integral 20th century modern art movements, beginning with cubism, heightening the authority of internet generated meme forms. MoMB presents the public with the unique opportunity to view, learn and interact with this emerging form.

data.name: Andy Schwetz Editions - Vol. 1 - For Ukraine
data.description:
This edition is a charity project whose proceeds are used to purchase and transport essential items for the people of Ukraine. 

I have a very deep connection to this Chernobyl exclusion zone. Not only because I could always enjoy the peace and quiet there. Not only because I love to explore the past. But mainly because my interest in the Chernobyl exclusion zone has tied me very closely to Ukraine and its wonderful people. 

Today I don't know if I will ever see this place again. Whether I will ever see the friends I made there again. Because where I once found peace and tranquillity, there are now tanks and soldiers. And my peaceful and friendly buddy is fighting them with Molotov cocktails. For his freedom, for the freedom of Ukraine and for our freedom.

I want to support these brave people. I owe them that.

SLAVA UKRAINI

この作品は、NFTアート「天使の卵」シリーズの第一作目です。
天使の卵〜予兆/空と海　5エディションです。
◯ストーリー
 2021年Covid19の流行で世界の多くの人々が不安に包まれている中、
地球上のいたるところに天使の卵が降り立ち、孵化の時をまっています。

天使はこの世に愛と癒しと平安をもたらすと言われています。
天使の卵は荒廃した世界にどんな世界をもたらすのでしょうか？

天使の卵は人間の目には見えませんが、たしかに存在しています。 すべての人の心に、私の心の中にも、そしてあなたの心の中にも存在しています。

天使の卵は、人の暖かい心を栄養として育ちます。 それに命を与えることができるか、死滅させてしまうかは一人一人の心にかかっています。

願わくは、新しい時代が、愛と赦しと平和に満ちたものとなりますように。
祈りを込めて。

※2021年、 Covid19の世界的なパンデミックで、多くの人々が不安に包まれているなか新しい時代の到来を告げるシンボルとして制作しました。

data.name: Animal Coloring Book
data.description: Animal Coloring Book is a Generative Transfer Art Project, building on [GTAP1](https://opensea.io/collection/wgtap1-og). On each of the first four transfers, a part of the image is colored. The color is determined by the address the NFT is sent to. On mint, the NFT is given one of six animal types, but is initially blank. On the fourth transfer, the Animal's mood is revealed - the coloring and animation of its eyes. The 10x10 SVG art and animation are generated and stored entirely on-chain. [Erasers](https://opensea.io/collection/animal-coloring-book-eraser) go with this project. Each eraser has a one time use to erase an image: resetting all colors and mood.

The 10x10 SVG art and animation are generated and stored entirely on-chain. [Erasers](https://opensea.io/collection/animal-coloring-book-eraser) go with this project. Each eraser has a one time use to erase an image: resetting all colors and mood.

data.description:
Welcome To The Jungle

The time has come for a new King or Queen to ascend the throne of Skull Island. The drums of war sound in the jungle, warriors across the animal kingdom have come to see who will achieve glory in combat. Armed with weapons and a hunger for ‘greatness’ the animals of Skull Island gather to see once and for all who the greatest warrior is. Will it be you?

7,777 warriors including Ape, Bull, Bear, Dog, Cat, Lion, Wolf, Fox, Elk, and Goat are ready to fight! Warriors can access the dual club or join a team to fight together. Every warrior has different abilities to cope with their battles. These abilities will be combined with an element of chance to determine the result. More exciting features will be announced and unlocked moving forward.
